      "date": "2013-06-28 21:05:06.000000000",
      "message": "Patch Set 1:\n\nThe interop test running a 2.1 server with master clients ( http://review.whamcloud.com/#change,6330 ) finally passes and shows that test 51b is skipped when the server version is less than 2.3.59.\n\nFor this patch, I'm not sure why testing was run twice. The first time autotest ran and all tests passed. The second time it just ran sanityn and failed due to LU-3360.\n\nI believe that this test is ready to review. Please let me know if there are any concerns.",
